{"tid":1396580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【前線軍樂建議】鼓手們入嚟睇吓樂譜","createTime":"2019-08-02T06:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:37:01.000Z","uid":16559,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a657e2476d3595c27421d79d0d046f34d5b83c85","tid":1396580,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"其實小弟我就唔係好多意見，純粹想將軍樂效果最大化，因為聲音係一種共鳴嚟，如果可以將佢同步進行會將威力倍化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！我極力推薦一首大家都識嘅樂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係Queen嘅We will rock you喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位鼓手進行軍樂演奏嘅時候請同附近嘅鼓手盡量配合演出，有助加強己方士氣。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係無聽過嘅朋友，以下係鏈結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-tJYN-eG1zk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-tJYN-eG1zk&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=63b58b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-tJYN-eG1zk</a><br />\n<br />\n樂譜頭兩下聲係相同嘅，第三下聲唔同就可以。當然實際現場做唔做到另一回事，唔啱聽嘅屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f8961179ebb05c56df10d38b0c759cc419d0657a","tid":1396580,"uid":16559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ebbbd3fff394699cc47e5d9bd8860d4a7452cc84","tid":1396580,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"前線頭盔/滅火裝備問卷調查!!!! 俾人扑過頭/滅過火  入黎無痕填一填!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/duticT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/duticT</a><br />\n全防具詳解&amp;購買連結 強烈建議睇 用PC開<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-s